  "texts": [
    "In addition to the ComVE dataset, we also semiautomatically constructed a new dataset named CSE, as detailed in Sect. 4.1.2.",
    "We performed experiments with various LLMs across these datasets, and the results consistently outperformed all strong baseline methods across all metrics.",
    "For instance, on the ComVE dataset, our method achieved superior performance with the OPT [28] model, significantly outperforming the strongest baselines.",
    "TIP demonstrated a 192% increase in METEOR score, a 204% improvement in ROUGE and a notable 631% increase in BLEU score compared to the highest performing baseline.",
    "These results clearly demonstrate the effectiveness of our proposed framework across various evaluation metrics.In summary, our contributions are as follows:• We present a novel two-stage identification and generation framework, TIP, for the commonsense explanation generation task."
